# Force LF line endings on checkout for text files. Without this, Windows
# CI runners (with `core.autocrlf=true` as default) check out `.kul` and
# other text files with CRLF, causing `kul format --check` and other
# byte-equality assertions to fail.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Belt-and-suspenders: explicitly mark known binaries so git never tries
# to "fix up" line endings on them.
*.png binary
